Tga '''Taflsuft''' nɣ '''Taflsaft''' yat tɣarast n uswingm ɣ umaḍal, iɣzwr, d wamun. tga tt asqsi n yan wanaw asilan n isqsitn f tumast (s [[Tutlayt Tafransist|tafransist]] d [[Tutlayt Tanglizt|tanglizt]] : ''essence'', ''nature'') n uswingm n ufgan, d tin iɣzwr, d wassaɣn illan gratsn.

Kra n twal, ar sawaln middn f "tflsaft iẓlin s yan". tga tt zɛma taɣarast nna s ittannay yan amaḍal. aṛtikl ad ur igi f "tflsafin ẓlinin s middn", is iga f tswingmin nna f msawln inflsafn tasutin f tasutin.

Kra ɣ isqsitn nna d fkan inflsafn gan tn:

* Ma'igan afulki?
* Is illa umaḍal ad anɣ issutln?
* Ma'igan taflsat?
* Ma'igan tayri?

== Azur n yism ==
'''Taflsuft''' nɣ '''Taflsaft''' (neɣ : ''' Tayri n tussna''') tga yat tguri d iwckan seg tutlayt [[Tutlayt Tagrikt|Tagrikt]] n zik, seg (φιλοσοφία, ''Filusufya''), taguri yad nzzḍar att nbḍu f snat tgzmin (Tigzmt tamzwarut :  φιλεῖν : ''Filyan'': iri neɣ Tayri, tigzmt tiss snat : σοφία : ''Ṣufya'' : Tussna neɣ tinẓeẓt : الحكمة ). Ɣiladd nzzḍar anini mas '''Taflsuft''' dars anamk n :  Tayri n tussna neɣ Tayri n tinẓeẓt.

